#: src/ch03-05-control-flow.md:566
msgid ""
"When you’re ready to move on, we’ll talk about a concept in Rust that "
"_doesn’t_ commonly exist in other programming languages: ownership."
msgstr ""
"Quand vous serez prêt à continuer, nous parlerons d’un concept en Rust qui "
"n’existe _pas_ couramment dans les autres langages de programmation : "
"l’ownership (la possession)."


