"echangeant les corps des blocs `if value < 1` et `else if value > 100` : "
"```rust,ignore,not_desired_behavior {{#rustdoc_include "
"../listings/ch11-writing-automated-tests/no-listing-09-guess-with-panic-msg-bug/src/lib.rs:here}} "
"```"

